## Context

- We use also Aceternity UI to style our application for modern and elegant components with animations.

## Rules

- You must use Aceternity UI for elegant components, for a landing page for exemple
- You must use Tailwind CSS for styling.
- You must install any AceternityUI missing component with `pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add https://ui.aceternity.com/registry/<component-name>.json`
